59:01.496 --> 59:03.623
- [Canister clanks]
- Oh! Oh! Oopsie! [Grunts]

59:03.707 --> 59:05.000
You dropped this.

59:05.042 --> 59:07.461
You know, I really better be
getting back to the grandkids.

59:07.586 --> 59:10.714
I mean, oh, god! The energy!

59:11.757 --> 59:14.217
What's that? The heck is that?

59:14.301 --> 59:16.303
- [Flare gun clicking]
- Is that a toy?

59:17.596 --> 59:20.098
No. It's a flare gun.

59:20.182 --> 59:21.516
What, for emergencies?

59:26.605 --> 59:28.273
I want you to tell the truth.

59:30.358 --> 59:31.985
I want you to say it.

59:33.361 --> 59:36.490
