01:04:33.495 --> 01:04:36.081
We'll be right back. Come on, girls.

01:05:06.945 --> 01:05:09.697
- [Door closes]
- [Sighs] Oh, Christ, no...

01:05:09.781 --> 01:05:11.533
Nurse!

01:05:15.286 --> 01:05:19.541
Joyce was away
visiting her mother, who was sick.

01:05:19.666 --> 01:05:24.087
