01:09:25.036 --> 01:09:27.038
[Crying]

01:09:35.963 --> 01:09:37.632
[Breathing heavily]

01:09:37.674 --> 01:09:39.258
[Moans]

01:09:43.388 --> 01:09:44.555
[Sobbing]

01:09:44.681 --> 01:09:47.684
["Afraid of nothing" continues]

01:10:24.429 --> 01:10:26.139
- [Bottle thuds]
- What?

01:10:26.264 --> 01:10:29.308
Oh. [Laughs] Did I wake you?

01:10:29.434 --> 01:10:30.893
- What's wrong?
- Nothing's wrong.

01:10:30.977 --> 01:10:33.855
